problem.markdown:
>>Which CUBE function defines a calculated set of members by sending a set of expressions to the cube, creates the set, and then returns that set to Excel?<<
( ) CUBEMEMBER ( ) CUBEVALUE (x) CUBESET ( ) CUBECOUNT
[explanation] The CUBESET function defines a calculated set of members or tuples by sending a set expression to the cube on the server, which creates the set, and then returns that set to Microsoft Excel. [explanation]
